OL,3,CIs the UK any nearer to making
OL,4,Cassisted dying legal?
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man has come one step
OL,7,Fcloser to legalising after the wording
OL,8,Fof the island's Assisted Dying Bill
OL,9,Fwas debated on Tuesday.
OL,11,FDr Alex Allinson, who is behind the
OL,12,FBill, said that after extensive debate
OL,13,Fand evidence taken from expert
OL,14,Fwitnesses, the island's parliament,
OL,15,FHouse of Keys (MHKs), approved
OL,16,F"another landmark step in delivering
OL,17,Fassisted dying".
