OL,3,CIs the UK any nearer to making
OL,4,Cassisted dying legal?
OL,6,FSo, as several parts of the British
OL,7,FIsles edge closer to legalising
OL,8,Fassisted dying, where does the UK
OL,9,Fstand? And what about the rest of
OL,10,FEurope?
OL,12,FWhat is assisted dying?
OL,14,FThe exact definition of assisted dying
OL,15,F- sometimes referred to as assisted
OL,16,Fsuicide or voluntary euthanasia - is
OL,17,Fstill debated among medical
OL,18,Fprofessionals, and each term has a
OL,19,Fslightly different meaning, but
OL,20,Fbroadly speaking it is the process of
OL,21,Fhelping a person to end their life.
