OL,3,CIs the UK any nearer to making
OL,4,Cassisted dying legal?
OL,6,FAssisted suicide is illegal under the
OL,7,FSuicide Act, which came into place in
OL,8,F1961, and it is punishable by up to 14
OL,9,Fyears in prison.
OL,11,FDepending on the circumstances,
OL,12,Feuthanasia is regarded as either
OL,13,Fmanslaughter or murder. The maximum
OL,14,Fpenalty is life imprisonment.
OL,16,Fis set to enter its first stage in
OL,17,F2024, after 36 MSPs backed the move.
