OL,3,CIs the UK any nearer to making
OL,4,Cassisted dying legal?
OL,6,FThe issue of legalising assisted dying
OL,7,Fwas last voted on in the House of
OL,8,FCommons in 2015, when it was defeated
OL,9,Fat the second reading stage by 330
OL,10,Fvotes to 118.
OL,12,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,13,Fsaid that he wants assisted dying to
OL,14,Fbe legalised after the next election.
OL,16,FSpeaking in March, Sir Keir said he
OL,17,Fwas "personally committed" to a change
OL,18,Fin the law.
