OL,6,FThat decision was then overturned in
OL,7,FFebruary 2020, making assisted dying
OL,8,Flegal again.
OL,10,FIn 2021 Spanish lawmakers legalised
OL,11,Feuthanasia and assisted dying for
OL,12,Fpeople who have serious, incurable or
OL,13,Fdebilitating diseases, and who want to
OL,14,Fend their lives.
OL,16,FBefore the ruling, anybody found to
OL,17,Fhave helped somebody to end their life
OL,18,Ffaced a prison sentence of up to 10
OL,19,Fyears.
