OL,3,CIs the UK any nearer to making
OL,4,Cassisted dying legal?
OL,6,FThe Netherlands brought its Euthanasia
OL,7,FAct into force in 2002, after the
OL,8,Fnational court concluded that the
OL,9,Faverage Dutch physician no longer
OL,10,Fconsidered it their duty to prolong a
OL,11,Fpatient's life under all circumstances.
OL,13,FBelgium passed a similar Act in the
OL,14,Fsame year, while Luxembourg followed
OL,15,Fsuit in 2009.
OL,17,FEach country has its own strict
OL,18,Fconditions under which assisted
OL,19,Fsuicide is considered permissible,
OL,20,Fsuch as stringent rules for physicians
OL,21,Fwho help with the procedure.
